transform_def.name: designed_3rd12
transform_def.string: let r = 1 / length(p_in) r1 = 2 / length(p_in) r2 = 0.5 / length(p_in) a1 = abs(tan(p_in.x)) - abs(tan(p_in.y)) a2 = sin(abs(p_in.x) - abs(p_in.y)) a = fmod(a2, a1) b = (abs(p_in.x + p_in.y) + abs(p_in.x - p_in.y)) z = tan(fmod(b, a)) / tanh(p_in.x * p_in.y) con0 = abs(z) > r1 con1 = abs(z) < r1 && abs(z) > r2 con2 = abs(z) < r2 in (if if fill <= 0.0 then con0 else if fill > 0.25 then con2 else con1 then p_in else vec2(0.0)) * weight
